    "aboutTitle": "Roadside Roots",
    "aboutText": [
      "Blacktop Brews started as a simple idea: good coffee, good people, and a whole lot of personality. We’re a small‑town, roadside stop with big flavor and zero pretension — the kind of place where your drink is made with care, your name is remembered, and the weather is always part of the conversation.",
      "We keep the classics you love, but we’re never afraid to shake things up. Every season brings new flavors, new experiments, and a little bit of controlled chaos — all crafted to fit the moods, storms, and backroads of Missouri life. Whether you’re rolling through for your daily pick‑me‑up or trying something bold, we’re here to make your day a little better (and a lot more caffeinated)."
    ],
    "contactTitle": "Pull Over & Say Hey",
    "contactText": "Got a question, a drink idea, or just want to say hi? I’m always happy to hear from the folks who keep Blacktop rolling.\nSend a message anytime — I’ll get back to you as soon as I’m done slinging lattes and arguing with the Missouri weather.",
